It's just amazing.

00:26:50.510 --> 00:26:52.330
Some very expensive ones,
some good ones.

00:26:52.330 --> 00:26:55.290
I mean, you can spend $1,000
easy, if you want to

00:26:55.290 --> 00:26:56.340
go to Per Se, too.

00:26:56.340 --> 00:26:59.190
It depends on the wine you buy,
or if you get into caviar

00:26:59.190 --> 00:26:59.940
or stuff like this.

00:26:59.940 --> 00:27:01.070
But you know what?

00:27:01.070 --> 00:27:04.380
I think it's even more expensive
in Europe now, those

00:27:04.380 --> 00:27:06.120
types of restaurants.

00:27:06.120 --> 00:27:07.710
Anyway, I didn't answer
your question, right?

00:27:07.710 --> 00:27:08.020
No.

00:27:08.020 --> 00:27:08.300
OK.

