ANJALI KUMAR: He has
a very diplomatic

00:27:09.640 --> 00:27:11.180
way of skirting around.

00:27:11.180 --> 00:27:13.340
You could be a lawyer
at Google.

00:27:13.340 --> 00:27:14.270
JACQUES PEPIN: Yes, thank you.

00:27:14.270 --> 00:27:15.230
ANJALI KUMAR: That was
very impressive.

00:27:15.230 --> 00:27:15.940
JACQUES PEPIN: That's
a compliment or--

